  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a retrospective study about serum Maresin-1 level in different severe acute
      pancreatitis patients. The investigators want to study the correlation between the level of
      serum Maresin-1 and the severity of SAP, of course the clinical outcomes. The investigators
      want to find some biomarkers and strategy target drugs of severe acute pancreatitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
